  - rowId: 1
    speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e5d83a1306f98a9cb2b27fde2681927, type: 2}
    textLines:
    - If this takes longer than a pint, I'm bust.
    - Ah, good to see an old freind - thiugh yer barely outta diapers. What can I
      get ye?
    - Joe took me tools again. I swear, I'll bury that bastard...
    - If ye break it, you but it. If I break it... well, that's a tradition.
